<br>
Norrath has much to offer me, and if indeed I find a companion, I hope it has much to offer you. I am looking for someone to travel the countrysides and the forests with, somebody to go on hunting exhibitions with, and somebody who is willing to take time out of their day to sit down at a tavern (Which tavern, of course, nobody knows) and drink an ale, speaking of the hunt and of our adventures.<br>
<br>
I plead to you, my fellow citizens, and I offer my friendship and my trust in return for yours, and hope that we can travel this land together.<br>
<br>
